## Direct Response Copy Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define the desired action (click, purchase, sign-up, call)
- [ ] 2. Identify the target audience and their primary objection
- [ ] 3. Apply direct response principles: headline, hook, offer, proof, urgency, CTA
- [ ] 4. Write copy that removes friction and creates momentum
- [ ] 5. Include urgency and scarcity elements
- [ ] 6. Test multiple headlines and offers

## Key Inputs
- Offer: {{offer}}
- Target Audience: {{target_audience}}
- Primary Objection: {{primary_objection}}
- Desired Action: {{desired_action}} (click, buy, sign up, call)
- Urgency Element: {{urgency_element}}
